This is a mirror of http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=2160

The package includes:

    vft.vim - the library
    vft-test.vim - simple plugin the utilizes the library

Screenshot of vft-test in action can be found here:

   http://javascript.cooldev.com/alx/vft.png

Lots of work yet to be done, but the library has minimal yet complete set of features that should simplify creation of simple forms.
